quran[9]{c,v,t}:
  3,62,"Pellet …óum …óoo, ko …óum woni fillayee goonga. Alaa dewetee…óo si wanaa Alla, pellet, Alla ko KaŇčko Woni Foolu…óo √Ďee√Īu…óo."
  3,63,"Si …ďe huccitii, pellet Alla ko ganndu…óo bonnoo…ďe …ďen."
  3,64,"Maaku: "Hey yim…ďe Defte, aree faade e konngol fotatngol hakkunde amen e mo'on : won de en ndewataa si wanaa Alla, en kafidataa Mo e huunde, wata yoga e me'en jogito yoga joomiraa…ďe ko woori Alla". Si …ďe huccitii, wi'ee: "Seeditee won de menen ko men jebbilii…ďe"."
  3,65,"Ee hey mon yim…ďe deftete, ko mbee√Īdaton e ge…óe Ibraahiima, Tawreeta e Linnjiila njppinaaka si wonaa …ďaawo makko : e on kaqqiltaa!."
  3,66,"Hey ko onon …ďee, on wennjii kon ko ganndal woodani on e mu'un, ko wennjaŇčton ko danndal alanaa on e mu'un? Alla no Anndi onon on nganndaa."
  3,67,"Ibraahiima laatanooki AlyahuuyaŇčke wonaana kadi Annasaaraajo, si ko woni, o laatinoke oo√Īii…óo [e kala diina] jebbilanii…óo [Diina Lislaamu], o laatanooki jeyaa…óo e shirkoo…ďe …ďen."
  3,68,"Pellet, ko …ďuri haadude e Ibraahiima e yim…ďe …ďen : ko …ďen jokku…ďe mo, e oo Annabiijo, e …ďen gom…óim…ďe. Alla ko Gi…óo gom…óim…ďe …ďen."
  3,69,"Fedde goo e yim…ďe Defte …ďen njidi nde …ďe majjina on, …ďe majjiŇčtaa si wanaa ko'e ma…ď…ďe …óen …ďe so'aa anndude."
  3,70,"Hey mon yim…ďe Defte, e ko njeddaŇčton Aayeeje Alla ∆äen tara onon ko on seedii…ďe?"